        {
            "id": 5967068,
            "title": "〈台股盤後〉整場白漲了逾百點 敵不過台積電尾盤豬羊變色 小跌3點作收",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>半導體關稅公布在即，美國聯準會公告利率按兵不動，台股今 (8) 日盤中一度大漲逾百點，最高漲至 20747.28 點，不過關稅政策尚未底定，市場觀望氣氛濃厚，在台積電尾盤由紅翻黑下，最後一盤爆出 263 億元，由上漲 134.94 點豬羊變色成小跌 3.09 點或 0.02%，以 20543.4 點作收，成交量較昨 (7) 日量縮至 2481.92 億元。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>電子權值股今天漲跌互現，台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 於最後一盤遭下殺由紅翻黑，爆出超過 7000 張的成交量，終場跌 10 元或 1.08%，收 918 元，鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 漲 0.69%，聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>) 漲逾 1%。另外，廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>) 跌 0.98%，台達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>) 漲逾 2%，日月光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3711\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3711-TW</a>) 漲逾 1%。 </p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美國商務部昨日證實，計畫撤銷拜登政府時期針對 AI 晶片出口的限制措施，激勵 AI 族群今天表現，代工廠方面，緯穎 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6669:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6669\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6669-TW</a>)、英業達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2356:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2356\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2356-TW</a>) 漲逾 2%，和碩 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4938:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4938\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4938-TW</a>) 漲逾 1%，緯創 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3231:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3231\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3231-TW</a>) 及仁寶 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2324:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2324\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2324-TW</a>) 也都小漲表態。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>伺服器機殼廠同樣走揚，晟銘電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3013:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3013\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3013-TW</a>) 漲勢凌厲，漲逾半根停板，勤誠 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8210:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8210\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8210-TW</a>) 漲逾 4%，迎廣 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6117:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6117\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6117-TW</a>) 漲逾 1%；散熱廠也勁揚，健策 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3653:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3653\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3653-TW</a>) 漲逾 2%，雙鴻 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3324:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3324\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3324-TW</a>)、奇鋐 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3017:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3017\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3017-TW</a>) 及建準 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2421:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2421\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2421-TW</a>) 也都有超過 1% 的漲幅。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台塑四寶 4 月營收 1 好 3 壞，僅南亞 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1303-TW</a>) 年月雙增，拖累今天表現，台化 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1326:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1326\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1326-TW</a>) 跌逾 4%，台塑 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1301:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1301\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1301-TW</a>) 及南亞雙雙跌逾 2%，台塑化 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6505:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6505\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6505-TW</a>) 則小漲 0.65%。另外，亞聚 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1308-TW</a>) 跌逾 3%，台聚 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1304:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1304\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1304-TW</a>)、華夏 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1305:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1305\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1305-TW</a>) 皆跌逾 1%。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
